  <h2 class="mt-2 font-mono text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold">Systems, not just commits</h2>
  <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-muted">
    Volume is easy to chart. This is the part that matters: what the client needed, how I modeled
